snippet.title: House of Berluscont: Early Gameplay (Scream Jam 2020)
snippet.description:
FULLSCREEN VIDEO TO REMOVE MOST ARTIFACTING!
YouTube's compression makes the dither effect look very bad, sorry.

This is early gameplay of my entry to Scream Jam 2020 (https://itch.io/jam/scream-jam-2020). An evidence-based murder mystery taking place in an unsettling manor.

See other stuff I'm doing: jacobknispel.com
